{"word":"ἀνέχω","slug":"ἀνέχω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἀνέχω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀνά\">ἀνά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἔχω\">ἔχω</a></el>] in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ NT\">NT</a> only <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ mid.\">mid.</a> <el>ἀνέχομαι</el> ‘put up with when faced with <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> disagreeable, annoying, or difficult’, <b><i>tolerate</i> <a href='B:470 17:17'>Mt 17:17</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ par.\">par.</a>; <b><a href='B:540 11:1'>2 Cor 11:1</a>, <a href='B:540 11:4'>4</a>, <a href='B:540 11:20'>20</a>; <a href='B:560 4:2'>Eph 4:2</a>; <i>endure</i> <a href='B:600 1:4'>2 Th 1:4</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ abs.\">abs.</a> <b><a href='B:530 4:12'>1 Cor 4:12</a>. <i>Bear with, listen to</i> <a href='B:510 18:14'>Ac 18:14</a>; <a href='B:650 13:22'>Hb 13:22</a>. <i>Be satisfied with</i> <a href='B:620 4:3'>2 Ti 4:3</a>.</b> Cp. the <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ opp.\">opp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Engl.\">Engl.</a> expression ‘I have had it.’ <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνευρίσκω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἀνεψιός\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}